    ==============================================================

         Welcome to the OlympicPhoneBox manager application

    --------------------------------------------------------------
     The purpose of this application is to provide an applicant
     interface for rendering of images and webcam feeds onto an
     LED curtain hardware using the LED T9 software.

     This project utilises the following libraries:
       o JavaCV - Java implementation of OpenCV
       o ProCamCaLib